    <h3 class="right_title">
      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/about/?2.html">潍博之信</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?3_1.html">规章制度</a></div>
      <span>规章制度</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">第九章  组织人事</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第一条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">本馆组织人事管理工作要自觉执行中共中央颁发的《党政领导干部选拔任用工作暂行条例》，规范干部的选拔任用工作，推进干部队伍</span>“四化”建设，形成“公道正派用人，用公道正派的人”的用人机制和管理制度。 </span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第二条</span> </span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">选拔任用领导干部工作，必须坚持以下原则：</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一、党管干部的原则。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二、德才兼备、任人唯贤的原则。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三、群众公认、注重实绩的原则。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">四、公开、平等、竞争、择优的原则。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">五、民主集中制原则。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">六、依法办事的原则。</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第三条</span> </span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">选拔任用领导干部，应坚持以下六条标准：</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一、坚决拥护党的路线、方针、政策，政治立场坚定。</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二、要全心全意为人民服务，有奉献精神。</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三、办事公道，作风正派，不以权谋私，在群众中有较高的威信。</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">四、能联系群众、团结同志，热爱党务工作。</span> </span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">五、进取意识强，勇于开拓创新。</span> &nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">六、年纪轻，有文化、懂业务、会管理，具有开创工作新局面的能力。</span> &nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第四条</span> </span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">选任干部和人事管理应遵守以下纪律：</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、不准以馆长办公会、领导圈阅等形式代替馆领导班子集体讨论决定干部的任免。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、不搞临时动议决定干部的任免。</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三、个人不能改变馆领导班子集体讨论作出的干部任免决定。</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">四、不准泄露酝酿讨论干部任免的情况。</span> </span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">五、不准在选任干部工作中封官许愿、打击报复、营私舞弊。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">六、考察材料不齐全，时间不充裕不讨论，不审批，不上报。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第五条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">选任中层以上干部，严格按照民主推荐，组织考察、党组织集体讨论决定、谈话、任职的程序。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第六条</span> </span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">干部的管理，应由组织人事部门按照干部管理权限，对其德、能、勤、绩等全面严格考察，重点考察工作实绩。每年定期进行考核。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第七条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">干部、职工的调进、调出，应经馆领导班子的集体讨论决定，人事部门按有关规定办理手续。</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第八条</span> </span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">干部的档案管理，按分级管理的原则。县处级领导干部的档案由市委组织部管理，科员以上的档案由政工科实施管理。及时将需要归档的材料按要求及时整理归档，做到不失、不漏。凡因工作需要，借阅人事档案的，要分管领导批准并办理借阅的有关手续。无关人员不准查阅干部档案。</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第九条</span> </span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">做好干部、职工的工资管理工作，按政策办理干部、职工的工资晋升等事项，做到及时、准确。</span></span></p><p><br/></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=471"></script></div>
      
      <div class="met_page">上一条：<a href="/content/?470.html">第十章  办公文秘</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;下一条：<a href="/content/?472.html">第八章  文创研发</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
